==German==
===Etymology===
Similar to {{L.}} ''[[cacare]]'', {{Gr.}} ''[[kakkao]]'', but possibly not directly related to these, instead [[onomatopoeic]], relating to the sound a baby makes when pressing while defecating ("a-a-").
